0527+  0216             ; THE 'LOAD-SAVE UPDATE' ROUTINE
0528+  0216             ; ------------------------------
0529+  0216             
0530+  0216             ; LOAD/SAVE
0531+  0216             SUB_0216:
0532+  0216 23              INC HL                              ; Step destination
0533+  0217 EB              EX DE,HL                            ; Backup to DE
