0564+  0240 21 96 43        LD HL,$4396                         ; Hard coded number we worked out before (start of program)
0565+  0243 C3 AC 04        JP L_04AC                           ; Re-initialise after loading and clear screen etc.
0566+  0246             
0567+  0246             ; ZX81-CONV-2
